Package: r4sub
Title: Easily Install and Load the R4SUB Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", email = "prm@outlook.in",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7864-5819"))
Description: The 'r4sub' package is a meta-package that installs and loads
    core packages of the R4SUB (R for Regulatory Submission) clinical
    submission readiness ecosystem. Loading 'r4sub' attaches 'r4subcore',
    'r4subtrace', 'r4subscore', 'r4subrisk', 'r4subdata', and
    'r4subprofile'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://r4sub.github.io/r4sub/, https://github.com/R4SUB/r4sub
BugReports: https://github.com/R4SUB/r4sub/issues
